===Noun===
'''clown''' (''plural'' '''clowns''')

#A [[performance artist]] who works in a [[circus]] and typically characterised/characterized by bright, [[oversized]] clothing, a red nose, [[face paint]], and a brightly coloured/colored [[wig]] and who performs [[slapstick]].
